title: Jennifer Westacott - Wikipedia

title: Dr Jennifer Westacott AO | Celebrating UNSW Women
snippet: Dr Jennifer Westacott AO has served as Chief Executive of the Business Council of Australia since 2011. She completed a Bachelor of Arts (Honours) in 1982 at UNSW and later received an Honorary Doctor of Letters, in 2017.
